# Content
This dataset contains a collection of high-quality images of various celebrities for face recognition research and development purposes. The images were sourced from various publicly available online platforms, and they feature different facial expressions, poses, and lighting conditions. The dataset is suitable for training and evaluating deep learning models for face recognition, facial expression recognition, and other related tasks. The images are labeled with the name of the celebrity in the filename, allowing for easy identification and classification.
